                                <entry>
<para>specifies the new state of the LSE. This parameter can be one of the following values: <itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_group___r_c_c___l_s_e___config_1ga6645c27708d0cad1a4ab61d2abb24c77">RCC_LSE_OFF</link> turn OFF the LSE oscillator, LSERDY flag goes low after 6 LSE oscillator clock cycles. </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_group___r_c_c___l_s_e___config_1gac981ea636c2f215e4473901e0912f55a">RCC_LSE_ON</link> turn ON the LSE oscillator. </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_group___r_c_c___l_s_e___config_1gaad580157edbae878edbcc83c5a68e767">RCC_LSE_BYPASS</link> LSE oscillator bypassed with external clock. </para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>
</entry>
